<plot>Shot in the mountains of Tibet, this film follows Professor Robert Thurman as he tours sacred sites, including Lhasa, the Potala Palace, The Nechung Monastery, Drepung, Gyantse, Shigatse, and then a trip around the sacred mountain of Mt. Kailsah, and a journey to the sacred Lake of Mansarovar.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?279870</url></doc>
